g.title: j2428447267
g.text: You're usually the super busy one. :)

g.title: j363362732
g.text: Ay, s√≠, jajaja I usually am

g.title: j3737841934
g.text: I've never had a real home, Lettie.

g.title: j3600620262
g.text: What do you mean, "someone like me?"

g.title: j671505866
g.text: The only places I've ever had to call "home" have tried to KILL me. Why would I miss them?

g.title: j1761370847
g.text: Because you can want something you never had
Or miss things you see other people having

g.title: j2419849647
g.text: Way to rub it in, Lettie. Thanks.

g.title: j3411297555
g.text: Can't miss what you've never had.

g.title: j3489172017
g.text: Details are different but you and me
Neither of us had a real home
Bouncing from place to place, base to base
Never settling, never making friends for long
Never knowing where I'd be in six months, a year, two

g.title: j1825076749
g.text: I grew up without a home and I get homesick

g.title: j523103034
g.text: I don't mean it like that

g.title: j2868755981
g.text: All I had were my family and their traditions
But sometimes I think they didn't even belong to me
Like you and those pinches orokin

g.title: j2902200609
g.text: At least you had your family, though. I didn't even have that.

g.title: j2978296857
g.text: You seem really proud of your background, I'm surprised.

g.title: j1234972538
g.text: How you aren't licking the wallpaper jaja
I have no idea I would have lost my mind

g.title: j1348014600
g.text: Being called slurs because of my skin or how I talk by everybody

g.title: j3479151562
g.text: I am because I learned no one can take it from me
But it took me a long time to get there

g.title: j2632613831
g.text: I miss a place and a thing I never had

g.title: j3481160695
g.text: See if you had it too
Maybe they fixed it by then

g.title: j626509248
g.text: No, I think I know how you feel. I... get these bouts of sadness where I get an urge to go somewhere that doesn't exist.

g.title: j1686551426
g.text: Maybe. I really don't get homesick. I get sad and lonely sometimes, but it isn't homesickness.

g.title: j2132032120
g.text: Or maybe we both have the same kind of depression jajaja

g.title: j4265733477
g.text: Maybe just my depression rearing its head again

g.title: j55194301
g.text: Speaking of spiders, time to put them and me to sleep
